INSERT INTO `node_revisions` VALUES(35, 70, 14, 'Materials @ Jeune Lune', 'According to Andrea''s post, we are set for Wednesday at 6pm at Jeune Lune. This could be a great opportunity to get materials, so thank you for setting this up! \r\nhttp://mapshanty.com/group/discuss/wednesday-november-12-jeune-lune-go\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>What do we do with the materials we buy on Wednesday?</strong>\r\nWe need to fill out a form with the art shanty crew in order to get our money. we''ll get $450 right away. The remaining $250 will be held until the end of the project (when our house is off the lake!) Lesley & I will initiate that process, but it won''t happen before Wednesday.  \r\n\r\nI am willing to float the money, and since I am in charge of the budget -- it probably makes sense to have one person taking it on. I suppose I should bring a wad of cash to Juene Lune. Do you think $200 bucks would do it?\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<strong>Any follow up on payment details by chance?</strong>\r\n\r\nI spoke with David, the art shanty dude, last night and it sounded like it was going to be possible for us to get into the Soap Factory ahead of time and store some things in the basement. The actual construction isn''t allowed to start until Dec 1.  I sent an email today and I''m waiting to hear back to see if they''ll confirm that we can get in by Wednesday night.  (we need a code to get in and a bit of orientation, i think)\r\n\r\nStay Tuned!\r\n', 'According to Andrea''s post, we are set for Wednesday at 6pm at Jeune Lune. This could be a great opportunity to get materials, so thank you for setting this up! \r\nhttp://mapshanty.com/group/discuss/wednesday-november-12-jeune-lune-go\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>What do we do with the materials we buy on Wednesday?</strong>\r\nWe need to fill out a form with the art shanty crew in order to get our money. we''ll get $450 right away. The remaining $250 will be held until the end of the project (when our house is off the lake!) Lesley & I will initiate that process, but it won''t happen before Wednesday.  \r\n\r', '', 1226385698, 1);
