INSERT INTO `node_revisions` VALUES(169, 241, 17, 'It''s that time again!', 'Hello shanty mappers!\r\nI hope this list still works!  I ran into both Alicia and Andrea this week and was reminded of what a wonderful adventure we had last winter.  It was the perfect thing to get me out of the house in the winter and make sure I didn''t spend all of my time sulking.  So, I''m writing to see if anyone has thought about doing it again?  The EXCO class applications for Fall are due next week, August 21.  If anyone is interested, we could apply for some funds from them and meet to figure out what kind of shanty we''d like to do this year and then apply to the art shanty project (anyone know when that is due?)\r\n\r\nI know it seems crazy to be thinking about this when it''s 90 degrees outside.  If you are interested in doing something, let me know.  Just thought I''d put the idea out there.  And if you''re interested in teaching anything else through EXCO this fall, the application is on our website: www.excotc.org.\r\n\r\nHope you''re doing well and staying cool!\r\nCallie', 'Hello shanty mappers!\r', '', 1250281101, 1);
